social_posts.post_text:
Starting 2023 in the studio 🙌🏼🎙️

Just 18 days left of being in my 30’s 😱😱😱😱

In bed by 10pm…I guess that’s what married life is about right? 

A perfect day marrying my perfect person ❤️

Bring on the party 🎉

How do you top ya wedding day?

Well, by having @djspoony at your party that’s how!!!! Absolutely insane night!!! ❤️
20.01.23 was absolute MAGIC! Married my best friend 💍🥰

*TRANSFER DEADLINE DAY NEWS*

New signing arriving in June! She can use either foot but known to stress the manager out…
Not sure who enjoyed the Easter egg hunt more…🐣🐰

Congratulations Hann, Casey & Zac! 

Welcome to our crazy gang Beatrice 🥰

It’s already a wonderful feeling being your Aunty & I can’t wait to always spoil you & look out for you forever ❤️❤️❤️❤️
A huge thanks to @plumbworld for kitting us out with these products for our house! We absolutely love them 🥰 #Ad
Summer days drifting away…🥰

With less than two weeks to go we thought we’d better build our pushchair which was kindly gifted to us by @icandyworlduk! We absolutely love it!!! ❤️❤️

We only nearly got divorced once which is pretty good going in the “build it yourself” jobs! 🤣 #icandypeach
Come on baby…we’re waiting for ya #MatchDay+7

*SUMMER TRANSFER NEWS*

Welcome to the world Gigi Elizabeth Akua Asante-Fisher. 

Born on June 28th at 1850, weighing in at a decent 8lbs. 

She already hates us for all the names but we couldn’t be more in love with her 🥰

A huge thanks to all the staff at the University Hospital of Wales for their amazing care & support ❤️

Celebrating a week of firsts & surviving it kinda 😂

✅ First week in the world 
✅ First walk & coffee out 
✅ First bath
✅ First solo night with Mummy (Mumma was away working 🥲)

And then there were three! Z, B & G all helping Grandma celebrate her birthday 🥰

Definitely no chance any of us will ever blow out our own candles again! 😂❤️

The longest, shortest, hardest, best month of our lives! 

4 weeks of Gigi 💗
Passport ready 😂📸
Double the months, double the size! ❤️ #Gigibear

Bebe’s & Gigi’s adventures continue…

Gigi’s first swim! All the gear no idea…👙

Thanks Uncle Rhys for letting us use your pool! 🥰
From first walks, to our first holiday, our iCandy Peach 7 pushchair has been with us every step of the way! #iCandyMoment
Hanging onto the sunny evenings ❤️☀️🍦

Happy 3rd birthday to our best boy, Zac! 

We all love you so much ❤️❤️❤️❤️

And well done @hannfish_hughes for another superb cake! 👨‍🚒 🔥

Not the score @fawales wanted but a night we’ll always remember as Gigi’s first ever football match! ❤️🏴󠁧󠁢󠁷󠁬󠁳󠁿 

So grateful she is able to watch & be surrounded by so many inspirational women 🤩…and @maurhys of course!!

3 months of Gigi Bear aka Super Koala 💕

Soz for the spam
Bay boat trip feat. ice creams & seagulls🛥️🍦
A third of a year gone already! Slow down time!! 💘

The chunkiest little skeleton you ever did see!

Happy birthday Oscar! 🎉❤️
Introducing G to the best people, wine & food 🥰❤️
Happy birthday to my dearest Nia. There’s not a single day that goes by that I don’t think about you and wish that we could meet again. Love you always ❤️❤️❤️❤️

It was never ever about awards but about making serious change and holding the Welsh Rugby Union and others to account. Thanks to the brave women and men we spoke to, I think that was achieved. And these awards are for you ❤️

A huge shoutout to Jayne & Karen who weren’t there last night- there’s no way the investigation would have happened without them. 

“Well behaved women seldom make history”

What an incredible night celebrating three legends of the game being inducted into the @barclayswsl Hall of Fame! 

I’m so proud of everything Neetz has done on and off the pitch and it’s amazing that she has been recognised by others to join an illustrious group of women. 

Huge congratulations to @jillscottjs8 & @ellsbells89 as well ❤️

Testing out the next stage of our @icandyworlduk MiChair ready for our weaning journey which starts this week! Have to say Gigi genuinely loves sitting in it which definitely helps relieve part of the stress! 🥰 #icandymoment
Campfires & sticks kinda day 🍂🥰

I genuinely think she thought she was being put on top of the tree! 😂 

Gigi’s first Christmas tree 🎄🥰

No reel will do this wedding justice! What a day 🎉 🍾

Congratulations Jess & Zee - love always wins ❤️❤️

Delayed 5 month photo due to our house being basically one big Petri dish 🧫😂

Giggles thanks to Hanny 🥰

When even Aunty Harriet & Marvin the monkey puppet don’t make the comedy grade for ya photo shoot 😂

Happy 6 months Gigi Bear 😍🥰
2023: The year of love ❤️
First swim in the sea for our little seal pup 🥹
